title: Colab : not recognizing labeled images after upload
body:
### Is there an existing issue for this?

- [X] I have searched the existing issues

### Bug description

I have labeled images locally on my laptop via the GUI and have then migrated to Colab to train the dataset and create the model.

However after upload to Google Drive and starting to train dataset the model is not recognising the labelled images.

All images have been labelled and the Collected Data CSV and Collected Data h5 files are existing in the source folder.

### Operating System

operating system

### DeepLabCut version

dlc version 2.2.0.5

### DeepLabCut mode

single animal

### Device type

gpu

### Steps To Reproduce

_No response_
